      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "While it seems to have the same resulting symptoms it doesn't always appear to require a chain of 25 unconfirmed transactions to start happening. Today we had hardly had any when it stopped working. Additionally there is no error, it just says low balance. \r\n\r\nThat being said I had not heard of this limit. Is there any mechanism to allow for more than 24 tx's between blocks as this seems like a huge limitation for business users? ",
