      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "Ok thanks for that. Say for instance I have 2 BTC in my wallet and 50 customers make a purchase in a space of 10 minutes, how is it possible to stop that being a chain? Its going to change the full balance for every tx and they'll all be unconfirmed and dependant on each other. Am I missing something? ",
