      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "Ah ok thank you very much. That sounds like the ideal solution, unfortunately we're using a variety of different manufactures of ATM/server and none of them have this functionality built in. They all handle each tx individually. Definitely something to pester them all about though! \r\n\r\nSo if there is not a flag to enable more I guess our only immediate option is to use multiple wallets to ensure we never go over the limit? ",
